Tuan Radha, Krishna,

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:15.760
tolong selamatkan aku hari ini.

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:19.120
Datang.

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:20.600
Ya.

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:24.240
Datang lebih cepat.
