00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:25.840
Datang.

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:32.160
'Sarla Mishra, Kepala Sekolah'

00:09:41.560 --> 00:09:42.720
Datang.

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:15.280
Halo Bu.

00:10:48.040 --> 00:10:49.000
Halo Bu.

