Mohan, bernapas saja.

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:34.280
Jangan terlalu bersemangat.

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:40.120
Tuan Trivedi, silakan datang dan duduk.

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:41.160
Tentu saja.

00:11:55.480 --> 00:11:58.080
Radha, ini sudah jam makan siang.

00:11:58.160 --> 00:11:59.760
Ayo pergi ke kantin
dan makan siang.

